&lt;p&gt;Noom is on a mission to help people live better, longer. We’re a consumer-led digital health company, connecting people to content, coaching, community, and clinicians, to build lasting habits and live healthier lives. We’re a high-growth organization powered by science, technology, and world-class talent. When you join Noom, on any team, you’ll see the impact of your work on the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Marketing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Noom, our Marketing team is the engine behind connecting millions of people to the products and programs that help them live healthier lives. We combine data-driven performance marketing with compelling storytelling to reach the right people at the right time—and inspire them to take action. Our team operates at the intersection of science, creativity, and technology, and the work we do has a direct, measurable impact on Noom’s growth and mission.&lt;/p&gt;
