&lt;li&gt;Oversee Microsoft advertising programs, ensuring strong performance and alignment with overall paid media strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Noom’s international paid social program across Meta, managing campaign strategy, execution, and optimization to drive efficient acquisition globally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and develop a direct report, coaching them on execution, building their skills, and helping them grow within the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze campaign, funnel, and conversion data to identify opportunities, inform strategy, and present findings clearly to senior stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Growth Product, Creative, and Engineering/Web Development teams to bring campaigns to life.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
