&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in performance or growth marketing, with ideally 1–2 years managing or leading others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on expertise in Google Ads and Meta Ads, with a track record of managing high-spend, direct response campaigns in-platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience running paid social programs across international markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with the ability to draw actionable conclusions from data; proficiency in Looker, Excel, or similar data visualization tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills, with confidence presenting strategy and results to senior leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative, cross-functional working style—comfortable partnering with product, creative, and technical teams to get things done.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in direct response (DR)-focused environments; experience at a performance marketing agency is a strong plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
