&lt;li&gt;Design and evolve social engagement loops to increase organic viral spread&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate behavioral science and user motivations into intuitive, compelling product experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create high-quality user flows, wireframes, prototypes, and polished visual designs that elevate the product experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with cross-functional teams to identify opportunities, shape product strategy, and define success metrics tied to business impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use data, experimentation, and iteration to continuously improve engagement and retention outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft thoughtful micro-interactions and moments of delight that reinforce positive behaviors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate design critiques and contribute to a high bar for design excellence and craft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
